arch veiled_woman
name Flora
msg
@match *
The Green Circle of Wizards was
developed to protect my forest. If it
weren't for my Green Circle,the Black
Alliance would overrun my kingdom. And
the White Circle? Ha! What have they
ever done. They are to busy squabbling
with the Black Circle. *sigh* Ever
since King Yoer disappeared things
haven't been right.
His son isn't ready for the throne. I
refuse to help their kingdom,those
advisors really rule that kingdom,not
the Prince.
At this you say,"How can you desert
your allies;if it weren't for the
kingdom of Yoer,your kingdom would be
invaded by the Forces of Darkoth.
Flora:I refuse to help them,they can
fight their own petty war. It was
those advisors fault Yoer disapeared.
(At this,Flora breaks down weaping.)
Flora:I must leave now...
(Flora flees the room.)
You think to yourself,"What could have
possibly happened to King Yoer."

endmsg
